# Jira Configuration Example
# Copy this file to `jira.env` (not committed) and fill in real values.

JIRA_USER=your-email@example.com
JIRA_TOKEN=your-jira-token-here
JIRA_INSTANCE=https://your-domain.atlassian.net

# Note: Do NOT commit `jira.env` with secrets. Use repository secrets or
# a secure vault in CI.
